libnemo-normalize (1.0.1-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging of libnemo_normalize.
  * Shared library with C API for NeMo text normalization via OpenFst.
  * Includes FAR grammar data for 19 languages (28 grammar sets).

